               <head>Judeo Persian biblical commentary</head>
               <msContents class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85013597">
                  <summary>Fragment of a Judeo-Persian commentary on portions of the Prophets.</summary>
                  <textLang mainLang="jpr" otherLangs="he" />
                  <msItem class="lccn.loc.gov/sh85013597">
                     <locus from="1r" to="33v" />
                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Perush ha-nevi᾿im</title>
                     <title xml:lang="he">פרוש הנביאים</title>
                     <note>
                        <p>Based on their content and linguistic and paleographic features, these
                  manuscripts are datable to the 11th-12th centuries, and not to the 16th century or
                  later as suggested by Margoliouth (information provided by Ofir Haim).</p>
                        <p>So far, it has not been possible to determine the identity of the authors of
                  these manuscripts and/or the place of their composition or copying. However, it is
                  quite possible to assume that the authors were Karaite since Hebrew Karaite terms
                  (e.g. רועי גלות, משכילים etc.) are attested in these texts. Another interesting
                  feature of these texts is their affinity to the commentaries of the Karaite Yefet
                  ben 'Eli. (Information provided by Ofir Haim).</p>
                     </note>
                     <filiation>The direct continuation of this manuscript is NLR Yevr.-Arab. I 4609 and
                NLR Yevr.-Arab. I 4607, f. 2.</filiation>
                     <msItem>
                        <locus from="1r" to="3r" />
                        <title>Commentary on Jer. 1:4-19</title>
                        <note>
                           <p />
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem>
                        <locus from="3r" to="10r" />
                        <title>Historical narrative concerning the kingdom of Judah</title>
                        <note>
                           <p>F. 3r: <quote xml:lang="he">סר אבדישת ישראלן</quote>.
                           </p>
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem>
                        <locus from="10r" to="10v" />
                        <title>A few accounts concerning the siege of Jerusalem and the destruction of the
                  Second Temple</title>
                        <note>
                           <p>F. 10r: <quote xml:lang="he">אני כאנה דויום אניז בד תר</quote>.
                           </p>
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem>
                        <locus from="10v" to="17r" />
                        <title>Commentary on Jer. 2:4-36</title>
                        <note>
                           <p>F. 10v: <quote xml:lang="he">תפסיר שמעו</quote>.
                           </p>
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem>
                        <locus from="17r" to="17v" />
                        <title>Miscellanea</title>
                        <note>
                           <p />
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem>
                        <locus from="17v" to="21v" />
                        <title>Commentary on Is. 57:14-58:14</title>
                        <note>
                           <p>F. 17v: <quote xml:lang="he">ענין כפור: ואמר סלו סלו</quote>.
                           </p>
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem>
                        <locus from="21v" to="24r" />
                        <title>Commentary on Is. 60:1-6</title>
                        <note>
                           <p>F. 21v: <quote xml:lang="he">תפסיר קומי אורי</quote>.
                           </p>
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem>
                        <locus from="24r" to="28v" />
                        <title>Commentary on Is. 60</title>
                        <note>
                           <p>F. 24r: <quote xml:lang="he">תפסיר ענין קומי אורי</quote>.
                           </p>
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem>
                        <locus from="28v" to="30r" />
                        <title>Discussion of evil speech</title>
                        <note>
                           <p>F. 28v: <quote xml:lang="he">סיפור גמול לשון הרע</quote>.
                           </p>
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem>
                        <locus from="30r" to="33v" />
                        <title>Commentary on Is. 61-62</title>
                        <note>
                           <p>F. 30r: <quote xml:lang="he">תפסיר ענין רוח יי אלהים
                  עלי</quote>.
                           </p>
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                     <msItem>
                        <locus n="33v" />
                        <title>The beginning of a commentary on 2Sam. 6</title>
                        <note>
                           <p>F. 33v: <quote xml:lang="he">תפסיר ענין ויוסף עוד דויד</quote>.
                           </p>
                        </note>
                     </msItem>
                  </msItem>
